title: Spider-Man 2 to be 'Empire Strikes Back' Dark - Kinda Funny Games Daily 09.29.21
description:
Greg and SnowBikeMike talk about how dark the Spider-Man 2 story will be, what's going on with the New World, and more!

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:03:50 - Housekeeping
PS I Love You XOXO LiS Spoilercast and Gamescast with Jared Petty!
NEXT WEEK, Blessing and Andy are taking part in Panda's All Star Nickvitational; a HUGE Nickelodeon All Star Brawl tournament featuring a bunch of big YouTubers and streamers like Ovilee, Moist Critikal, Ludwig, and more. It's all to raise charity for The Breast Cancer Research Foundation.
Andy and Bless need YOUR help. Competitors in the tournament and their communities have 1 week to raise money to bid on their favorite character. That's based on the money you donate. Right now you can go to kindafunny.com/bless and kindafunny.com/andy to donate so the guys can bid on the character of their choice. And remember that money all goes to The Breast Cancer Research Foundation.
The tournament is happening on Tuesday, October 5th at noon PT on Twitch.tv/pandaglobal.
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: The Kinda Funny Destiny 2 PC Clan & Black Jack
The Roper Report  -
00:06:02 - Spider-Man 2 Will Be “Empire Strikes Back” Dark, Jared Moore @ IGN
00:24:10 - New World Order
00:45:28 - Netflix Buys Night School, Sean Krankel
00:53:28 - Halo PC Concerns and Comments, Eddie @ GameSpot
00:77:50 - Super Monkey Ball Review Round-Up
00:42:25 - Ad
00:58:45 - Out today
01:03:00 - Squad Up:Jordan Lee Rowan(PS5) - LikeARowanStone
01:04:00 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts: Tam and Tim
